name: The Onyx Feather Swarovski + Vintage Jewelry Club
description:
How it works:

1. Purchase jewelry club membership for a recipient of your choice.  ($120)

2. Within 24 hours receive a five-question style survey about the recipient (ex: Is the recipient's style classic, modern, eclectic, quirky etc); this will serve as a guide for Onyx Feather to design & scout the perfect earrings for the recipient. 

3. Each month (for a period of 6 months) the gift recipient will be pleasantly surprised with a beautifully packaged alternating pair of 100% vintage or hand-crafted Onyx Feather Swarovski earrings in the mail.  (Three sets of vintage & three sets of customized Onyx Feather earrings altogether). Styles range from jeweled studs, to tear drops & chandelier earrings. Each set of earrings will be from an Onyx Feather city collection. (Current collections are Cairo, Paris, Cyprus, Rio de Janeiro and St. Petersburg). 

Details:

Shipping is included in the purchase price. Please allow three works from date of purchase for the first pair of earrings to ship. Recipient will receive an email announcing membership within 48 hours of purchase unless purchaser requests otherwise. 

Please note: gift club membership cannot be refunded after check out; however, it can be exchanged for store credit within 7 days.

Interested? Have questions?
Contact: inquiries@onyxfeatheronline.com for more information.

Fifteen percent of your purchase supports the Legacy Scholarship Fund of Invisible Children. Visit www.onyxfeatheronline.com for more information.
